I"<h2 id="install-pluging">install pluging</h2>

<p>add to Gemfile <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">gem 'jekyll-admin', group: :jekyll_plugins</code></p>

<p>run <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">bundle install</code></p>

<h2 id="access">access</h2>

<p>run <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">bundle exec jekyll serve</code></p>

<p>go to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">localhost/admin/</code></p>

<p>we can manage our website from this page</p>
:ET